<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Timeline base on WF2W</title>
</head>
    <body>
        <span>Time line base on [<a href="https://github.com/dcsoft-yyf/WF2W">https://github.com/dcsoft-yyf/WF2W</a>],
        and source code at [<a href="https://github.com/dcsoft-yyf/WF2W/tree/main/WinForms/OpenSource.DCTimeLineForWinForm">https://github.com/dcsoft-yyf/WF2W/tree/main/WinForms/OpenSource.DCTimeLineForWinForm</a>].</span>
        <div dctype="System.Windows.Forms.Screen"
             style="border:3px solid black; width:100%; height:800px;
                font-family:宋体; font-size:12px; background-color:skyblue"
             EntryPoint="RunDCTimeLine">
            <span style="color:yellow;font-size:20px">Loading...</span>
        </div>
        <script src="DCResourceStrings-zh-cn.js"></script>
        <script src="_framework/blazor.webassembly.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>